iez une situation et une expression.", "words": [81, 82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87]}, {"id": 25, "text": "1.", "words": [88]}, {"id": 26, "text": "Nous sommes le janvier.", "words": [89, 90, 91, 92]}, {"id": 27, "text": "a.", "words": [93]}, {"id": 28, "text": "Tous mes vœux de bonheur!", "words": [94, 95, 96, 97, 98]}, {"id": 29, "text": "2.", "words": [99]}, {"id": 30, "text": "Léa est invitée à dîner chez des amis.", "words": [100, 101, 102, 103, 104, 105, 106, 107]}, {"id": 31, "text": "b.", "words": [108]}, {"id": 32, "text": "Bon voyage !", "words": [109, 110, 111]}, {"id": 33, "text": "3.", "words": [112]}, {"id": 34, "text": "Agnès a eu une promotion.", "words": [113, 114, 115, 116, 117]}, {"id": 35, "text": "c.", "words": [118]}, {"id": 36, "text": "Joyeux Noël!", "words": [119, 120]}, {"id": 37, "text": "4.", "words": [121]}, {"id": 38, "text": "Matthieu part en vacances.", "words": [122, 123, 124, 125]}, {"id": 39, "text": "d.", "words": [126]}, {"id": 40, "text": "Qu'est-ce que je peux apporter ?", "words": [127, 128, 129, 130, 131, 132]}, {"id": 41, "text": "5, Solange va se marier.", "words": [133, 134, 135, 136, 137]}, {"id": 42, "text": "e.", "words": [138]}, {"id": 43, "text": "Bonne année !", "words": [139, 140, 141]}, {"id": 44, "text": "6.", "words": [142]}, {"id": 45, "text": "Nous sommes le 24 décembre.", "words": [143, 144, 145, 146, 147]}, {"id": 46, "text": "f.", "words": [148]}, {"id": 47, "text": "Toutes mes félicitations !", "words": [149, 150, 151, 152]}, {"id": 48, "text": "7.", "words": [153]}, {"id": 49, "text": "Didier part en voyage.", "words": [154, 155, 156, 157]}, {"id": 50, "text": "g.", "words": [158]}, {"id": 51, "text": "Bonnes vacances !", "words": [159, 160, 161]}, {"id": 52, "text": "32 Choisissez la bonne explication.", "words": [162, 163, 164, 165, 166]}, {"id": 53, "text": "1.", "words": [167]}, {"id": 54, "text": "«Repose-toi bien !", "words": [168, 169, 170]}, {"id": 55, "text": "» 4.", "words": [171, 172]}, {"id": 56, "text": "« Mon pauvre René !", "words": [173, 174, 175, 176, 177]}, {"id": 57, "text": "»", "words": [178]}, {"id": 58, "text": "a.", "words": [179]}, {"id": 59, "text": "Odile va dormir.", "words": [180, 181, 182]}, {"id": 60, "text": "a.", "words": [183]}, {"id": 61, "text": "Rose plaint René.", "words": [184, 185, 186]}, {"id": 62, "text": "b.", "words": [187]}, {"id": 63, "text": "Odile part en vacances.", "words": [188, 189, 190, 191]}, {"id": 64, "text": "b.", "words": [192]}, {"id": 65, "text": "Rose félicite René.", "words": [193, 194, 195]}, {"id": 66, "text": "2.", "words": [196]}, {"id": 67, "text": "«Toutes mes félicitations !", "words": [197, 198, 199, 200]}, {"id": 68, "text": "» 5.", "words": [201, 202]}, {"id": 69, "text": "« Ça va, Lucien?»", "words": [203, 204, 205, 206]}, {"id": 70, "text": "b.", "words": [207]}, {"id": 71, "text": "Louise va à un examen.", "words": [208, 209, 210, 211, 212]}, {"id": 72, "text": "b.", "words": [213]}, {"id": 73, "text": "Adèle est amie avec Lucien.", "words": [214, 215, 216, 217, 218]}, {"id": 74, "text": "6.", "words": [219]}, {"id": 75, "text": "«Salut, Gabriel !", "words": [220, 221, 222]}, {"id": 76, "text": "»", "words": [223]}, {"id": 77, "text": "a.", "words": [224]}, {"id": 78, "text": "Louise a un nouveau travail.", "words": [225, 226, 227, 228, 229]}, {"id": 79, "text": "L] a.", "words": [230, 231]}, {"id": 80, "text": "Adèle ne connaît pas bien Lucien.", "words": [232, 233, 234, 235, 236, 237]}, {"id": 81, "text": "3.", "words": [238]}, {"id": 82, "text": "« Enchantée, monsieur !", "words": [239, 240, 241, 242]}, {"id": 83, "text": "»", "words": [243]}, {"id": 84, "text": "a.", "words": [244]}, {"id": 85, "text": "Béatrice connaît bien Paul.", "words": [245, 246, 247, 248]}, {"id": 86, "text": "a.", "words": [249]}, {"id": 87, "text": "Luc dit bonjour ou au revoir.", "words": [250, 251, 252, 253, 254, 255]}, {"id": 88, "text": "LU UD LL", "words": [256, 257, 258]}, {"id": 89, "text": "b.", "words": [259]}, {"id": 90, "text": "Béatrice ne connaît pas Paul.", "words": [260, 261, 262, 263, 264]}, {"id": 91, "text": "b.", "words": [265]}, {"id": 92, "text": "Luc dit bonjour.", "words": [266, 267, 268]}, {"id": 93, "text": "| 4 2 Faites le dialogue entre les deux personnages.", "words": [269, 270, 271, 272, 273, 274, 275, 276, 277, 278]}, {"id": 94, "text": "> treize + 13", "words": [279, 280, 281, 282]}]}